<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
	<link href = "https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../music.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../style.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../chat.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../landing.css">
</head>

<body>
	<%- include("navbar") %>
	<%- include("music") %>

	<div id="landing">
		<!-- heading -->
		<header>
			<div id="heading">
				<!-- explain value you provide -->
				<h1>JournAl: An AI Journaling Application</h1>
				<!-- explain how you'll create value -->
				<p>Developed to increase overall happiness, and ultimately, improve mental well-being, this AI powered journal provides suggestions for you while you write and analyses your emotions.</p> 
				<div id="action">
					<a href="/signup"><button class="signup">Sign Up</button></a>
					<p>Backed by research and based on HarvardX's Managing Happiness course</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- some sort of image -->
		</header>

		<!-- features and benefits -->
		<div id="features">
			<div class="featureSection">
				<img class="image" src="../images/business-success-chart.svg">
				<div class="description">
					<h4>Journal Analysis</h4>
					<p>Provides suggestions on your journal entries to help you talk through your feelings and ideas, which helps improve overall happiness.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="featureSection">
				<div class="description">
					<h4>AI Therapist Chatbox</h4>
					<p>The build-in AI chatbox acts as a therapist and guides your thoughts, enabling you to talk with someone about how you feel.</p>	
				</div>
				<img class="image" src="../images/work-from-home.svg">
			</div>

			<div class="featureSection">
				<img class="image" src="../images/happy-man-waving.svg">
				<div class="description">
					<h4>Sentiment Analysis</h4>
					<p>The integrated LLM scans for your emotions in your journal entry and provides a summary in your profile page, allowing you to see your total mood and how you've been feeling over time.</p>	
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div id="end">
			<h3>Try the AI Journaling Application Now!</h3>
			<a href="/signup"><button class="signup">Sign Up</button></a>
		</div>
	</div>


	<script src="../js/music.js" defer></script>
	<script src="../js/chat.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>